metadata.name: Full sails
metadata.description:
Schooner Opal crossing King Oscar fjord in Greenland - one of the most remote places in the whole world. I remember myself standing on another vessel and seeing this moment through my camera, and it felt like I had a time machine and traveled back in time where people had no electric power but they had real adventures.

All profit from this NFT goes to support artists who coming from Ukraine/Russia to California. 
I personally work on this project, providing food, shelter and financial support for any artist who lost their home because of the war.
